column5: I am heading to Upsala, Ontario on June 29-July 5 and was wondering if anyone could reveal useful information on fishing Lac des Mille Lacs. It will be my first time there and any information that would assist in catching some big walleyes would be appreciated.
Kellee,Tell me where you are staying and I'll see if I can help. Won't be responding to you until 6/26, as I am headed to LDML to meet up with a party of ten. I'll help you if I can.
